        "在淫荡地喘息的同时，她继续摆动着腰部。",
        "她的动作不仅没有停下来，甚至还更加用力。",
        "而且似乎陷入了狂热之中，屁股肉紧紧地贴在一起，施加了重量。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_022",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_022.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呜呜，嗯哦，嗯呼！啊啊，啊呜呜！",
        "里面，好痛，啊啊，肉棒好厉害！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但是，一点也不痛苦。",
        "相反，被压制住反而感觉很舒服。",
        "还有被责难的兴奋感。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_023",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_023.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈，哈，哈！嗯嗯，嗯呼，嗯哦哦！",
        "一直，一直到最深处，都要被填满啊，啊啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "每次枫抬起屁股，我的肉棒也会被拉扯起来。",
        "阴道和肉棒紧密地贴在一起。",
        "当肉棒顶到最深处时，感觉就像吸盘一样吸住了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_024",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_024.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊啊，太厉害了，太刺激了，小穴太受不了了！嗯啊啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "挑逗我的态度消失了，现在完全专注于我的肉棒。",
        "她猛烈而淫荡地摆动着腰部，充分享受着快感。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_025",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_025.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「这样下去，小穴会被撑得无法回复了！",
        "这肉棒的形状，我会记住的！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她的表情也变得淫荡起来，嘴角还流下了口水。",
        "她的腰使越来越激烈。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_026",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_026.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「这种感觉，好像是第一次！一下子，就要……来了！",
        "意识都被肉棒占据了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "看起来，她正朝着巅峰迈进。",
        "我这边也快到极限了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "lines": [
        "「我也差不多了……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "说完，枫的眼睛闪亮起来。",
        "就像一只凶猛的肉食动物面对猎物时的眼神。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_027",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_027.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「好啊！来吧，来吧，射出来！！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她一边喘息着，一边挑逗着我。",
        "她的腰部动作也变得更加锐利，为了让我射精。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・快感我慢",
        "file": "EV038_04"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_028",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_028.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯哦，哦哦，噢呜！在小穴里抽插，感觉舒服吗？」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她一边挑逗着，自己也感到强烈的快感。",
        "越来越兽性的喘息声，刺激着我的耳朵。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_029",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_029.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈呜，呜呜，嗯哦哦！快点！",
        "嗯嗯，啊呜！要，要射了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "大概枫自己也到极限了吧。",
        "从她的表情和声音可以看出她已经无法忍耐了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_030",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_030.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呜！嗯呼！哈，哈！不，不行了！忍不住了，要射了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "一边口中喊着高潮，一边猛烈地动着腰部。",
        "肉棒在紧紧缠绕的阴道中摩擦着，强烈的刺激扩散到下半身。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_031",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_031.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「快点，快点射出来！哦呵呵！",
        "大力地射精出来吧！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "确实有种比拼忍耐的感觉。",
        "虽然并不在意胜负，但作为男人，我想先让枫高潮。",
        "然而她的阴道却在努力让我射精，给予我强烈的快感。",
        "紧紧地缠绕着，扭动着，吸附在龟头上。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "lines": [
        "「呜呜……已经……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_032",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_032.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「要射了，要输给肉棒了！",
        "啊嗨嗨！要高潮了，高潮了～呜呜！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "小穴紧紧地收缩着。",
        "当我知道枫已经达到高潮的瞬间，我也射精了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔",
        "file": "EV038_05"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8201B",
          "file": "se/8201b.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "嘭噗噗！哗哗哗！"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_033",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_033.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呜！哦呵呵！精液，射出来了！",
        "热热的，射进了小穴里！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "她大声喊着，一下子坐下来。",
        "她的体重压在我的身上。",
        "肉棒的顶端紧贴着子宫口。",
        "哗哗哗！嘭噗！嘭噗噗！！",
        "然后，我继续坚定地射精注入其中。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_034",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_034.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊呜呜！射进子宫里了！",
        "哦哦，好厉害！哦呵呵～！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "平时不曾见过的颓废表情。",
        "枫在高潮的呼喊声中，像发情的雌兽一样喘息着。",
        "当然，在射精的同时，她的腰仍在不停地动着。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_035",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_035.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈，哈！出来了，好热啊！",
        "嗯呼呼！哦呵呵，嗯哦哦～！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "肉棒的顶端紧贴着子宫口，我扭动着腰部，一边挤压着精液。",
        "刚刚才在翼的小穴里射精过，结果又射出了大量的精液。",
        "不，应该说是被迫射精了。",
        "完全被榨干了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_036",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_036.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯咕咕！哈哈！太厉害了！",
        "嗯嗯嗯，嗯哈啊～！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "射精结束后，她还在用力抵着我。",
        "好像在挑逗我再射出更多一样。",
        "真的已经没有更多了。",
        "她似乎也明白了这一点，终于平静下来，减缓了腰部的动作。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・アヘ顔・精液",
        "file": "EV038_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_037",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_037.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈啊啊……真是一次了不起的射精……果然，年轻人的劲头不一样呢……啊呜呜！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・うっとり妖艶・精液",
        "file": "EV038_07"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8331A",
          "file": "se/8331a.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "似乎还在享受余韵，她的腰部缓慢地动着。",
        "小穴紧紧地收缩着，继续刺激着我的肉棒。",
        "然后，枫说了一句话，思考了一下。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・うっとり妖艶・精液",
        "file": "EV038_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "楠木枫",
      "voice": {
        "id": "KAED_007_KAED002B_038",
        "file": "voice/kaed_007_kaed002B_038.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯，比赛的结果算是平局吧？",
        "我们两个一起达到了高潮呢。」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV038・うっとり妖艶・精液",
        "file": "EV038_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_KAED_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_kaed_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
